ea - Expense Add

USAGE:
    ea [-category=category]

DESCRIPTION:
    Add an expense record. Prompts for expense details including
    description, category, and costs. Automatically calculates totals.

OPTIONS:
    -category=category
        Set expense category

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-expenses-text-fields FIELDS
        Text fields for expense records

    -conf-expenses-numerical-fields FIELDS
        Numerical fields for expense records

EXAMPLES:
    ea
    ea -category=groceries
    ea -category=entertainment
